snippet.title: The Daedalus Encounter trailer
snippet.description:
This trailer is for a 1995 video game/interactive movie called The Daedalus Encounter, starring Tia Carrere.

The file is a Cinepak/PCM QuickTime file found on the Windows 3.x game disc. Converted natively by YouTube. Unfortunately, the sync is not correct but it's difficult to notice in this video.
